name: Corn Daze
description:
Corn Daze is here!

Collect all the corn before the time runs out, but beware of the corn holes, if you get too close you will begin again!

Corn Daze is a labyrinth-type maze game that will have you biting your nails to beat the clock. 

 Hope you enjoy!

Game created by: Monique Alexander

Music Used by: 

Forest Walk by Alexander Nakarada | https://www.serpentsoundstudios.com
